[Hook: Fabolous]
I see dead people
I see dead people

I see dead people
I see dead people
I look in my pocket and I see dead people

One (one), two (two), three (three), body count
One (one), two (two), three (three), everybody count

[Verse 1: Fabolous]
More bodies I'm back for more bodies

I'm running and I know's it

[Bridge: Fabolous]
I see dead people
I see dead people
I look in my pocket and I see dead people

[Hook]
